Hello, Welcome to my bloxorz game.

Instructions:

1. You need to fall through the hole in the center.
2. Do not stand upright on a green tile.
3. The red tiles are switches that activate/de-activates bridges in the game.
4. The scoreboard is ticking at the top-right corner.

Controls:

Keyboard:

w - move forward
a - move left
s - move right
d - move down
w/a/s/d+space - skip a tile in that direction
t - tower view
p - top view
l - level view
b - block view
f - follow cam view
h - helicopter view

Mouse:

Left_button_click+drag - move in helicopter view
Mouse-scroll - increase/decrease height


